# Tenant Services Chatbot â€“ Documentation

## Overview
This project is a Tenant Services Chatbot built using Python and Streamlit to help tenants with FAQs, complaint registration, and hostel/PG rules.

## Features
- FAQ handling (rent, rules, leave)
- Maintenance complaint registration
- Admin view for complaint tracking
- Emotion-aware responses (creative feature)

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Streamlit
- SQLite

## Setup Instructions
1. Clone the repository
2. Install Streamlit
   python -m pip install streamlit
3. Run the application
   python -m streamlit run app.py

## Usage
- Ask questions related to rent and policies
- Report maintenance issues
- View complaints in admin section

## Future Scope
- Generative AI integration
- Voice-based chatbot
- Authentication for admin
